name: RABBIT HOLE
description: Anyone who is a constant web search knows what its like to go down a rabbit hole and finding yourself not being able to find your way back. This project is a web app with a simplistic design that allows users to save their search results and come back to them later.

name: Filopino Community Signup form
description: This project is a signup form for the Filipino community to assist in gathering user data for fintech app in development, this form is being launched at this years festival with over half a million attendees.

name: Blue Kee Design Co.
description: This project is for a local digital designer who is looking to showcase their work and attract new clients. The site is a simple one page design that showcases the designers work and provides a contact form for potential clients.

name: Devin Runowski
description: This project is my Software Engineering portfolio. It showcases my work and provides a way for potential employers to contact me.
